commit_comments.body:
Sorry, I wasn't explicit enough.

Say I have the following document

``` json
12345.Test
{
  "Id": "12345",
  "Prop1": "Value2"
}
```

Model

``` csharp
public class Model
{
  [JsonProperty("Id")]
  public long Id { get; set; }

  [JsonProperty("Prop1")]
  public string Prop1 { get; set; }
}
```

This line would forcibly inject `"id":"12345.Test"` (just because my `*I*d` is capitalized) - and the deserialization is compromised.

